Text: Thanks Extremezone. as always no need to ask about A/V im sure its as good as all your other ops

I took an oath never to watch a movie that has two actresses with the first name of Kristen in it.  According to ancient Mayan texts, when two actresses named Kirsten star in a movie, all who watch it will suffer a curse of unbearable agony.  

But even though I am unable to see this movie, I want to thank extremezone for his exceptional service to the community.  Enjoy all!
